{"tid":1927518,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【反擊】沒有人因為武漢肺炎而歧視武漢人，但會因政權刻意隱瞞而歧視該國人。","createTime":"2020-03-15T22:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T09:06:14.000Z","uid":263448,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3182b26614b13daebc993c077aafaf13eeb4da65","tid":1927518,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T22:40:43.000Z","msg":"極短回應「武漢肺炎就是歧視中國人」文宣戰：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有人因為武漢肺炎而歧視武漢人，<br />\n但會因政權刻意隱瞞而歧視該國人。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正如，<br />\n沒有人因為香港腳，而歧視香港人。<br />\n沒有人因為日本腦炎，而歧視日本。<br />\n沒有人因為德國麻疹，而歧視德國。<br />\n極權政府因為掩飾、自卑心作祟，而刻意隱瞞、淡化，必然賠上整個國家和國民，長遠聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>藍絲群都可以應用：<br />\n沒有人因為肺炎而歧視武漢人，<br />\n盡管叫法不同，但我們心繫祖國。<br />\n好人一生平安</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">防疫用：<br />\n沒有人因為武漢肺炎而歧視武漢，<br />\n但我會因為你不戴口罩而鄙視你。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c431fd2270519d32ff7771dd6ba6f0687062287e","tid":1927518,"uid":263448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T22:59:17.000Z","msg":"抗爭者專用：<br />\n沒有人因為武漢肺炎而歧視中国人，<br />\n因為我們一早歧視你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ae18d5413b688710daed82022b3ccfd06b474b","tid":1927518,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T02:47:01.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ac0496d1a439cc153ff8719b5b5533268ac4e5b6","tid":1927518,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T06:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ff2739cba49f5ac785a104369ce48dc533175d","tid":1927518,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T09:00:54.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3126867884bd58211a3a6e7f6b1abe2e8fc8e2ef